## PrepareTransferUnsignedPsbtParams interface

Parameters required to generate an unsigned PSBT (Partially Signed Bitcoin Transaction) for transferring RGBPP assets. This interface is used to estimate transaction fees before finalizing the transaction.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export interface PrepareTransferUnsignedPsbtParams 
```
